His flagship restaurant, Wild Rocket, specializes in what Low describes as "mod sin" or modern [Singaporean cuisine](/wiki/Singaporean_cuisine). [Diners Club](/wiki/Diners_Club) named Wild Rocket one of the top 50 restaurants in [Asia](/wiki/Asia). Before entering the restaurant industry, Low [practiced law](/wiki/Lawyer) for eight years.
